Uwamwezi Violette yayoboye [[DOT Rwanda]] kuva yashingwa mu mwaka wa 2010. Mbere ya DOT Rwanda, yamaze imyaka irindwi muri Ambasade y’u [[Rwanda]] i Washington DC, atangira ari umusesenguzi wa politiki maze arazamuka aba umudipolomate ku mwanya w’Umunyamabanga wa mbere. Arangije ubutumwa bwe, yoherejwe muri Minisiteri y’ububanyi n’amahanga ya [[Kigali]], ashinzwe ibihugu bya [[Aziya]] na [[:en:Oceania|Oceania]].

== Amashuri ==
Violette afite impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga mu buyobozi bwa Leta (Master’s Degree in Public Administration) yibanda ku iterambere mpuzamahanga ryaturutse muri kaminuza ya Carleton [https://carleton.ca/ (Carleton university]) yakuye mu igihugu cya [[Kanada|Canada]] na Bachelor of Arts mu by'ubukungu no guteza imbere igereranya ryaturutse muri kaminuza ya Trent [https://www.trentu.ca/ (Trent university])

== Amateka ==
Violette ni umunyamuryango wa Afrika Leadership Network (ALN) akaba yarahawe igihembo cya Anita Borg Institute Change Agent Award ya Grace Hopper Celebration y'abagore muri Mudasobwa. Muri 2016, Violette yagizwe umwe mu bagore 25 ba mbere b'icyubahiro ba Amazon's Watch Magazine muri Afurika kubera ibikorwa bye byo guteza imbere ubukungu abakobwa n'abagore bakiri bato.Ni umujyanama mu [https://www.imbutofoundation.org/ Imbuto Foundation] ikigo cyashinzwe na Madamu wa Perezida wa Rwanda na [https://mastercardfdn.org/our-work/where-we-work-in-africa/rwanda/ MasterCard Foundation] Young Africa Work, kandi agira uruhare mu guteza imbere ubukungu bw’urubyiruko n’abagore ndetse n’iterambere ry’ikoranabuhanga.

== Ibihembo yahawe ==
Muri 2013 yahawe igihembo na ANITA BORG INSTITUTE cya ABIE CHANGE AGENT AWARD, Iki gihembo cyatanzwe mu rwego rwo gushimirwa ubwitange yagize ku ruhare rw'umugore mu gihe kizaza cy'u Rwanda n'ikoranabuhanga mu itumanaho no guhanga udushya muri Afurika, no guteza imbere abakobwa bakiri bato mu ikoranabuhanga no kubamenyesha amahirwe n'imyuga mishya mu ikoranabuhanga, kwihangira imirimo ndetse no mu mishinga ishinzwe imibereho myiza. 

2014 yahawe igihembo cy'abagore Bakomeye muri Afurika Mubucuruzi na Guverinoma no Kwishimira kuba indashyikirwa mumashyirahamwe (CEO).Iki gihembo cyatanzwe mu rwego rwo gushimirwa ibyagezweho nkuwatsinze mu burezi no mu mahugurwa: Abikorera ku Rwanda mu Kinyamakuru Umuyobozi mukuru w’abagore bakomeye mu bucuruzi no mu bihembo bya Leta.

